Section Header: Coordinator:  TRAINING MODEL #1 sitting upright: Keen ON, GRD OFF; Train the Keen on the following 4 behaviors sitting upright (GRD already pre-trained on these behaviors).
Item Header: I will ask you to perform different actions with your right hand. Please try to act naturally as you perform each of the actions.  We’ll start by calibrating the devices on your wrist.
Field Label: First, pretend to scratch or pull hair on the back of your head until I tell you to stop.
Now pretend to scratch or pull hair on the right side of your head above your ear until I tell you to stop.
Now pretend to pull your right eyelash until I tell you to stop.
Now pretend to bite your nails until I tell you to stop.

Section Header: Coordinator: TRAINING MODEL #1 sitting upright: Keen ON, GRD OFF; Train the Keen on the following behavior in 3 positions (GRD already pre-trained on this behavior).
Field Label: Once again, pretend to bite your nails until I tell you to stop.
Now lean back and look up at the ceiling and pretend to bite your nails until I tell you to stop.
Finally, lie on your left side and pretend to bite your nails until I tell you to stop.

Item Header: Okay, we’re done with calibration. Next, we’ll repeat these actions, but this time I want you to place your right hand on your lap, perform the action I ask you to do for 5 seconds, then place your hand back down on your lap.  Okay, let’s start with your right hand on your lap.
